{"tid":1546504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候忘記Do you hear the people sing","createTime":"2019-09-06T09:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T11:09:46.000Z","uid":72476,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"03039413f13ec56dc8cc1d8855d81ba326a8db0f","tid":1546504,"uid":72476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:55:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=58361abb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Do you hear the people sing始終唔係屬於我地自己既歌<br />\n由今日開始！大家一齊背熟呢首代表香港人既歌！<br />\n他日香港立國！呢首一定係我地既國歌！<br />\n我唔知要等幾多年，唔知自己有冇仲等到個日，但我深信個日一定會來臨！<br />\n加油呀！香港人！<br />\n光復香港！！！時代革命！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"baf3d1ba0a44ee45cc6c464f83e9942843bbe2f2","tid":1546504,"uid":72476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:57:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4adeecd805642449bf5a6a043b99708de9a8e797","tid":1546504,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:57:34.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fg5HKFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFg5HKFh.jpg&h=b79850f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=d125822d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"135b714bd4265737aa882106739e0d5153182244","tid":1546504,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:58:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61acc8b85